{"tid":1521872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再射藍水, 情況許可記得拎水樽打包兩枝","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:17:58.000Z","uid":119157,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"272528ad36ba5ef228d5e55b3f0292d8e1386050","tid":1521872,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:08.000Z","msg":"拎比D警察子女家屬睇下<br />\n嘩唔甩色架幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cccee9ed9ab25d2bb2b558fe82b5187ecbb06c5","tid":1521872,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. hot sodium carbonate solution<br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾<br />\n<br />\n3.化妝水/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行"},{"pid":"c98ee2b21fc87d1d4a9c033336e8b117e0462cae","tid":1521872,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc5be8d08b299f4e5f350e59091bea56e08c5cc","tid":1521872,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"好提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856c0b06d16954b6e8b041d69843b800be591db9","tid":1521872,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb21fef51da9ba8bacbee037f12f5eb2352fc4fa","tid":1521872,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=5c64541e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=356401b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=c264ec77\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"10438e08b5ef6d2a658acd60a1c2d0cd82081c48","tid":1521872,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2